with a solar system.

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:53.200 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah.

00:14:53.200 --> 00:14:56.060 align:middle line:10%
And the number is
just astonishing.

00:14:56.060 --> 00:14:57.700 align:middle line:10%
