universe of 246 trillion stars.

00:15:02.980 --> 00:15:07.210 align:middle line:10%
Well, a certain percentage
of those, like 90-something%

00:15:07.210 --> 00:15:10.210 align:middle line:10%
are red dwarfs, which we
think might be habitable.

00:15:10.210 --> 00:15:12.560 align:middle line:10%
Then another few percent
are orange dwarfs-- type K

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:13.360 align:middle line:10%
orange dwarfs.

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:16.240 align:middle line:10%
And then you get
our sun, a type G.

00:15:16.240 --> 00:15:18.970 align:middle line:10%
That's the majority of
those stars are habitable.

00:15:18.970 --> 00:15:22.600 align:middle line:10%
It's-- again, the numbers just
don't allow us really to be

00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:26.230 align:middle line:10%
alone, especially-- and it can
get worse because we don't know

00:15:26.230 --> 00:15:28.060 align:middle line:10%
what the geometry
of the universe is.

00:15:28.060 --> 00:15:32.020 align:middle line:84%
But it appears to be a sort of
flat geometry, as they call it.

00:15:32.020 --> 00:15:35.230 align:middle line:84%
And that just simply means
that if you run a railroad

00:15:35.230 --> 00:15:39.320 align:middle line:84%
track across the universe,
the tracks will never meet.

00:15:39.320 --> 00:15:42.610 align:middle line:84%
So it's a-- just a geometry
just like we're familiar with.

00:15:42.610 --> 00:15:44.110 align:middle line:90%
It seems to be flat.

00:15:44.110 --> 00:15:47.740 align:middle line:84%
That could have the implication
of three different geometries,

00:15:47.740 --> 00:15:49.370 align:middle line:90%
but one of them is infinite.

00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:52.180 align:middle line:84%
And if the universe is infinite,
there's not only alien life,

00:15:52.180 --> 00:15:54.430 align:middle line:84%
there are exact
copies of us outside

00:15:54.430 --> 00:15:57.160 align:middle line:84%
of the observable universe, and
there are an infinite number.

00:15:57.160 --> 00:15:57.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Two.

00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:59.620 align:middle line:90%
