00:16:50.540 --> 00:16:53.270 align:middle line:10%
And this was
discovered in the 1960s

00:16:53.270 --> 00:16:57.830 align:middle line:10%
as having a very chemically
anomalous makeup.

00:16:57.830 --> 00:16:59.660 align:middle line:84%
