00:29:08.460 --> 00:29:12.540 align:middle line:84%
And that is the 1420
megahertz hydrogen line.

00:29:12.540 --> 00:29:17.370 align:middle line:84%
Neutral, natural hydrogen
emits radio at that frequency.

00:29:17.370 --> 00:29:20.940 align:middle line:84%
