00:29:20.940 --> 00:29:22.290 align:middle line:90%
at that frequency.

00:29:22.290 --> 00:29:24.000 align:middle line:90%
Anybody with science knows that.

00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:26.640 align:middle line:84%
No matter where they are
in the observable universe,

00:29:26.640 --> 00:29:28.382 align:middle line:84%
they know about that
radio frequency.

00:29:28.382 --> 00:29:30.090 align:middle line:84%
So that would be a
good place to put one.

00:29:30.090 --> 00:29:33.660 align:middle line:84%
And that's exactly where we
